snippet.title: Introducing JigsawPuzzles.io - Free Online Multiplayer Jigsaw Puzzles!
snippet.description:
Free multiplayer jigsaw puzzles for you and your friends!

JigsawPuzzles.io provides a new way for puzzle fans all over the world to unite and cooperatively solve puzzles together.

We've hand-picked thousands of beautiful, high-quality, family-friendly images from a variety of talented amateur and professional photographers across the globe. This new-meets-old concept brings cooperative online multiplayer to a gaming tradition that people have enjoyed for centuries.

Piece together a scenic beach setting from the Spanish Riviera, or check out the vibrant colors and lights of Tokyo's metropolitan sprawl. JigsawPuzzles.io brings some of the world's most breathtaking vistas and locales right into your browser - one piece at a time!

Check it out at: jigsawpuzzles.io

----------------------------------------------------------------

Music credit: Happy, by MBB
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/mbbofficial
